Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:26.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(240,0)}阴差阳错入深宫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:32.72,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(240,0)}天边楼宇今咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:39.83,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(240,240)}浮世纷繁方知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:45.36,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(240,0)}难解疑案频接踵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.74,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(240,0)}奇想妙解豁然开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:01:00.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,240)}柳暗花明又一村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:05.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(240,0)}往日何曾思明日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:08.14,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,240)}含苞蓓蕾始方绽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:12.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(240,0)}此般岁月亦安然
